Actions.Text: AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO GOVERNMENTAL EMPLOYEES

Title: Authorizes the town of Seneca Falls to offer an optional twenty-year retirement plan to a certain formerly employed police officer
Summary: Authorizes the town of Seneca Falls to offer an optional twenty-year retirement plan to Jamie Buffone under section 384-d of the retirement and social security law.
ActClause: AN ACT to authorize the town of Seneca Falls to offer an optional twenty-year retirement plan to a certain formerly employed police officer
